ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: Code to identify the general type of benefits under which products and services are provided.

ivardefs.name: detail_
ivardefs.desc: The plan/proposal/order describing the proposed service in detail.

ivardefs.name: diagnosis_
ivardefs.desc: Patient diagnosis for which care is sought.

ivardefs.name: facility
ivardefs.desc: Facility where the services will be provided.

ivardefs.name: modifier_
ivardefs.desc: Item typification or modifiers codes to convey additional context for the product or service.

ivardefs.name: productOrService
ivardefs.desc: This contains the product, service, drug or other billing code for the item.

ivardefs.name: provider
ivardefs.desc: The practitioner who is responsible for the product or service to be rendered to the patient.

ivardefs.name: quantity
ivardefs.desc: The number of repetitions of a service or product.

ivardefs.name: supportingInfoSequence_
ivardefs.desc: Exceptions, special conditions and supporting information applicable for this service or product line.

ivardefs.name: unitPrice
ivardefs.desc: The amount charged to the patient by the provider for a single unit.

properties.desc: Service categories or billable services for which benefit details and/or an authorization prior to service delivery may be required by the payor.
